{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408580/extras/game.gif?t=1737741061\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i>Rome: Nightmares of  Empire is an <strong>Action</strong> game with <strong>RPG</strong> elements, <strong>charming pixel graphics</strong> and <strong>interesting mechanics</strong>.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Story</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><i><strong>year 70, Judea, the province of the mighty Roman Empire</strong></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The legions, led by the emperor's son, <strong>Titus Flavius</strong>, had just captured <strong>Jerusalem</strong>, the largest city of the rebels, and turned the tide in the war to their side. As a legionnaire, you are now heading towards the fortress of\u00a0<strong>Machaeron</strong>, another place engulfed in <strong>uprising</strong>.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">But something stops you...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">During the fights, you meet a strange, higher-ranking soldier armed with Roman equipment. It turns out to be the infamous <strong>Cestius Gallus</strong>, who was defeated at the beginning of the war and <strong>killed</strong>. Somehow he <strong>rose from the dead</strong>. You are tasked with finding out why...\u00a0</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Goal</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Defeat your opponents, <strong>acquire</strong> and <strong>create</strong> equipment, <strong>improve your skills</strong> to face the great threat, <i>rise up, <strong>hero and save Rome\u00a0</strong></i>!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408580/extras/gif1.gif?t=1737741061\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Gameplay</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The <strong>Gladius</strong> sword, <strong>Scutum</strong> shield and <strong>Pilum</strong> javelin together with <strong>the divine support of the Roman gods</strong>, Jupiter and Minerva, Mars and Pluto, Vesta and Mercury and <strong>dexterity</strong> and <strong>perseverance</strong> will be your weapon against the rebels in <strong>Judea</strong>, the barbarians in <strong>Germania</strong> and <strong>Galia</strong> and the well-trained Carthaginians in <strong>Italia</strong>!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Camp</u></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Being alone in endless enemy areas, you need to be prepared. And the best place to do this is a camp full of soldiers and merchants. Watch out for one of them, he's a crook! You will also find answers to key moments in the plot here...</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3408580/extras/gif2.gif?t=1737741061\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><u>Elements</u></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 13 different history-inspired bosses!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 60 different items!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Over 60 different achievements!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">4 Roman provinces with different opponents!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Extensive skill tree</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Creating and upgrading items</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Targets board</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Missions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Plot</p></li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Welcome to camp!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3408580/9d03ff95b8e8711a399b6bfc8391dba0c6985d18.jpg"},{"name":"Roman citizen!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3408580/067e0b74dfc6198681941512fc41e20d21b4d5f5.jpg"},{"name":"Germania !","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3408580/504bb52807ff47949e258d1cb2eceb8fdb05351a.jpg"},{"name":"Galia !","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamc